---
title: Vietnamese-Style Pork Meatball Banh Mi with Potato Wedges & Crispy Shallots
description: Inspired by the loveable Vietnamese sub, this version will take you to the streets of Hanoi on the first bite. Smear over
a garlic aioli and pack in some sweet and soy pork meatballs to balance out the carrot noodle slaw. To add something a bit different, serve with a side of wedges, perfect for dipping in aioli if you have extra leftover.
